{"type": "article", "id": 10718, "title": "Allsteel Mimeo with IntelliForm™ 办公椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-12T06:48:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110900Nfqv0j9GShITDYPo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<span>看</span><span>起来好像与其它办公室的转椅没有太大的不同，只是后背增添了网格状的设计，其实这是 </span><span>Allsteel Mimeo </span><span>设计的一款新兴办公椅，符合人体工学，深度挖掘了当今材料与制造工艺的潜力，</span><span>Mimeo </span><span>使用独特的 </span><span>IntelliForm™</span><span>  </span><span>后背工艺技术，提供最理想的弹性和个人化的舒适度。</span><span>3D </span><span>的表面如同皮肤，摸起来不是冰冷的，并且透气舒适。塑料撑架能适应人体不断变化的姿势，提供支撑力。而座椅下的金属支柱包含重量调节装置，能将人的重量转移到地面上。办公椅整体很轻，加上底部灵活的转轮，可以自由移动。并且有多个配色可选择，设计者想打造一种更轻松和具有美感的办公环境。<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021108587UdY9MDEmZ13OBgo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.35568182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110859vix7OwYefsz0XqhA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110859VSY3UfKsXoejNBah.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110900PW0dhFvnAU7SOJiw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\n\n"}